13070.name: 스핀 커터

17220.name: Lance of Judgment
17220.desc: Summon a gigantic spear of light at the target location, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:172202/> [Holy] Damage and launching foes into the air. Crit Rate +<FONT COLOR='#99ff99'><$MACRO buffstat0_100 @1:172200/>%</FONT> for all party members within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10-meter</FONT> radius for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10s</FONT>.

17800.name: Defensive Stance
17800.desc:
Activate Defensive Stance using your Shield Meter. While in Defensive Stance, incoming attacks drain Shield Meter instead of HP. However, in exchange for toughness, Move Speed -<FONT COLOR='#ff9999'>50%</FONT>.
Defensive Stance slowly consumes your Shield Meter, and it will be deactivated when your Shield Meter runs out.

17820.name: Battlefield Shield
17820.desc:
Consume all Shield Meter and move instantly to a location up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>16 meters</FONT> away, ignoring collisions with Adventurers, Guardians, and monsters.
Upon landing, strike foes and inflict <$MACRO physic @1:178401/> Damage to foes within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6-meter</FONT> radius, launching them into the air. Foes within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3-meter</FONT> radius of the center of impact suffer a direct hit.
Gain a shield proportional to the consumed Shield Meter, and grant Push Immunity to party members within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10-meter</FONT> radius. Any Damage to them will be directed to you for up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>5s</FONT>. If you stop using Battlefield Shield or if the Shield is attacked and disappears, Condensed Energy explodes and deals <$MACRO physic @1:178404/> Damage to nearby foes before knocking them away. Damage dealt by the explosion can increase up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>30%</FONT> based on the amount of Damage blocked on behalf of allies. Cannot be used when Shield Meter is below <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>20%</FONT>. When Battlefield Shield expires, Shield Meter is refunded a minimum of <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10%</FONT> and up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>40%</FONT> based on the amount of Damage blocked on behalf of allies.

18011.name: Vortex Gravity
18011.desc: Strike your hammer downward, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180200/> Damage and exploding gravitational energy in front of you, which inflicts<$MACRO Magic @1:180210/> Damage and pulls in foes within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6-meter</FONT> radius. The downward strike with the hammer can be <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>counterattacked</FONT>.

18020.name: Run
18020.desc: Sprint forward with a lowered posture. You can use other skills while sprinting.

18025.name: Stand Up
18025.desc: When you've fallen, roll forward and quickly stand up.

18026.name: Stand Up
18026.desc: When you've fallen, roll forward and quickly stand up.

18050.name: Heavy Crush
18050.desc: Raise your hammer above your head, then smash the ground with a downward attack, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180501/> Damage. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>1</FONT> Gravity Core.

18060.name: Gravity Impact
18060.desc: Strike your hammer downward, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180601/> Damage, and start injecting Gravitational Energy where you stand. Gradually pull and attack foes <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8</FONT> times for a total of <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 180602/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 180602/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 180602/>)/2))*4/></FONT> Damage, then cause a gravitational explosion that pulls foes close inflicting <$MACRO magic @1:180603/> Damage. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Cores.

18070.name: Full Swing
18070.desc: Strike behind you with your hammer and spin <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>360</FONT> degrees, attacking surrounding foes <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3</FONT> times in total, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180700/>, <$MACRO physic @1:180701/>, and <$MACRO physic @1:180702/> Damage. Overcharge to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:180703/> Damage.

18080.name: Earth Smasher
18080.desc: Swing the hammer above your head in a circle and strike the ground, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180800/> Damage and creating a huge boulder. Take a swing at it to break it and propel the fragments in a cone-shaped blast, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180801/> Damage. Foes hit by the rock fragments are stunned for <$MACRO bufftime_st @1:180803/>s. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3</FONT> Gravity Core.

18090.name: Earth Wave
18090.desc: Quickly move <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6 meters</FONT> and charge up to 3 times, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:180900/> Damage in total. Raise your hammer and strike the floor to create a cone-shaped wall <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2 times</FONT>, each inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:180901/> and <$MACRO Magic @1:180903/> Damage, respectively.

18100.name: Neutralizer
18100.desc: Imbue your hammer with gravitational energy and swing it downward with might, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181000/> Damage. This ground smash causes a shockwave within an <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8m</FONT> radius, inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:181004/> Damage. Use the skill again to hit the ground <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> more times, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181001/> and <$MACRO physic @1:181002/> Damage. Shockwaves inflict the same amount of Damage.

18110.name: Dreadnaught
18110.desc: Take a ready stance with your hammer on your shoulder, concentrating your energy on your Cores, and then hit the ground to send forth a shockwave, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181100/> Damage, and use the momentum to jump high. While jumping, slam your hammer down onto foes, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181101/> Damage. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Core.

18120.name: Terra Break
18120.desc:
Hammer the ground in front of you, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181200/> Damage and knocking down all foes within range. Swing your hammer upward to create anti-gravity and inflict and <$MACRO magic @1:181204/> Damage. All foes within range are shot into the air. Concentrate your energy and jump, hammering foes flat to the ground with a hammer and anti-gravity attack that inflicts <$MACRO physic @1:181206/> and <$MACRO physic @1:181207/> Damage, respectively.
This skill restores your Gravity Meter <FONT COLOR='#99ff99'>100%</FONT>.

18130.name: Seismic Hammer
18130.desc: Hold your hammer upside down, then jump and smash the ground, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181300/> Damage. The crash forms a cone-shaped wall that stretches <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>11</FONT> meters, inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:181301/> Damage.

18140.name: Endure Pain
18140.desc: Let out a roar, inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:181401/> Damage to foes within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6-meter</FONT> range. Upon using the skill, gain a buff that makes you immune to Pushes and incoming Damage -<FONT COLOR='#99ff99'><$CALC_COMMA <$TABLE_SKILLBUFF PassiveOptionValue0 181400/>/100/>%</FONT> for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'><$CALC_COMMA <$TABLE_SKILLBUFF Duration 181400/>/1000 /></FONT>s. When hit by a boss of a specific rank or higher, Penalty Meter -<FONT COLOR='#99ff99'>50%</FONT>. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3</FONT> Gravity Cores.

18150.name: Earth Eater
18150.desc: Smash the ground behind you, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181500/> Damage, then spin around with chunks of rocks following your hammer. Spin a total of <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3</FONT> times, each spin inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181501/>, <$MACRO physic @1:181502/>, and <$MACRO physic @1:181503/> Damage. Your hammer goes higher with each spin until you swing it down to the ground to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:181504/> Damage.

18160.name: Jumping Smash
18160.desc: Leap to the target location within <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10 meters</FONT> and swing your hammer down to the ground, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181600/> Damage. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Cores.

18170.name: Perfect Swing
18170.desc: This skill can be charged for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>1.4s</FONT>. When used mid-attack, you will advance <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3 meters</FONT> forward as you swing your hammer with both hands to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:181700/> Damage. Overcharge the skill to move <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>4 meters</FONT> forward and deliver an even fiercer blow to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:181702/>Damage.

18180.name: Power Strike
18180.desc: Raise your hammer above your head and smash the ground <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3</FONT> times, each smash inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181800/>, <$MACRO physic @1:181801/>, and <$MACRO physic @1:181802/> Damage. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Core.

18190.name: Gravity Compression
18190.desc:
Thrust your hammer into the ground and release a gravitational wave while inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:181900/> Damage.
Hold for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2s</FONT> to release a black hole, inflicting <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 181901/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 181901/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 181901/>)/2))*9/></FONT> Damage over up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>9</FONT> hits. If you stop holding before the Holding Meter is maxed out, the black hole explodes and inflicts <$MACRO Magic @1:181910/> Damage within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>5-meter</FONT> radius. Max out the Holding Meter to cause a bigger explosion, inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:181911/> Damage to foes within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6-meter </FONT>radius.

18200.name: Gravitational Energy
18200.desc: Hold your hammer close to the hammerhead and swing it at foes in front of you, inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:182000/> Damage. Afterward, your hammer releases Gravitational Energy, attacking foes in a straight line <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>7</FONT> times for a total of <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 182001/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 182001/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 182001/>)/2))*7/></FONT> Damage, pulling them close. Foes affected by the energy receive <$MACRO Magic @1:182002/> Damage and become forcefully pulled to a nearby position. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Core.

18201.name: Gravitational Energy
18201.desc: Hold your hammer close to the hammerhead and swing it at foes in front of you, inflicting <$MACRO Magic @1:182000/> Damage. Afterward, your hammer releases Gravitational Energy, attacking foes in a straight line <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>7</FONT> times for a total of <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 182001/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 182001/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 182001/>)/2))*7/></FONT> Damage, pulling them close. Foes affected by the energy receive <$MACRO Magic @1:182002/> Damage and become forcefully pulled to a nearby position. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Core.

18210.name: Running Crash
18210.desc: Hold to sprint forward and charge at foes, inflicting up to <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA ((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 182103/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 182103/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 182103/>)/2)) * 5) + ((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 182104/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 182104/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 182104/>)/2))*2)/></FONT> Damage over <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>7</FONT> hits. The Gravitational Energy explodes when you release the skill key or max out the Holding Meter, launching foes into the air for <$MACRO Magic @1:182100/> Damage. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Core.

18220.name: Power Shoulder
18220.desc: Crouch and charge <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>5 meters</FONT> forward with your hammer held in front of you, attacking <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>4</FONT> times to inflict <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 182200/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 182200/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 182200/>)/2))*4/></FONT> total Damage. Use as a combo to raise the hammer high and inflict <$MACRO physic @1:182201/> Damage, launching foes into the air. On hit, obtain <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>2</FONT> Gravity Core.

18230.name: Big Bang
18230.desc: Gather Gravitational Energy then explode it, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:182300/> Damage to foes in a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3.2meter</FONT> radius and knocking them away. All incoming Damage -<FONT COLOR='#99ff99'>50%</FONT> and gain immunity against Status Ailments, Pushes, and Move Speed Reductions. Ignore collisions with adventurers and normal monsters while gathering energy. You can move while gathering Gravitational Energy. Damage up to +<FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 182300/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 182300/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 182300/>)/2))*2/></FONT> and the explosion radius up to +<FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8 meters</FONT>, depending on how long you gathered energy.

45004.name: Bloodlust
45004.desc: Quickly slash at foes in front of you to inflict <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 451400/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 451400/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 451400/>)/2)))+(((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 451401/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 451401/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 451401/>)/2))*3)+(((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 451402/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 451402/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 451402/>)/2)))/></FONT> Damage, then perform a powerful stab, knocking them away for <$MACRO physic @1:451403/> Damage.

45010.name: Dash
45010.desc: Lower your body and slide <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8 meters</FONT> as you move quickly.

45011.name: Wild Dash
45011.desc: Lower your body to an attack stance and slide approximately <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6 meters</FONT> as you move quickly.

45012.name: [뿌리클래스] 회피
45012.desc: Lower your body and slide <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8 meters</FONT> as you move quickly.

45020.name: Stand Up
45020.desc: When you've fallen, roll forward and quickly stand up.

45050.name: Fury Blade
45050.desc: Jump and swing your greatsword to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:450500/> Damage and launch foes into the sky, then strike down to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:450501/> Damage and knock them down.

45060.name: Wild Rush
45060.desc: Charge <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>7 meters</FONT> toward the target location and inflict <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 450600/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 450600/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 450600/>)/2)))+(((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 450601/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 450601/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 450601/>)/2)))+(((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 450602/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 450602/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 450602/>)/2)))/></FONT> Damage to foes in your path.

45070.name: Hurricane Sword
45070.desc: Spin around for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3</FONT>s to inflict up to <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 450700/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 450700/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 450700/>)/2)))*12/></FONT> Damage.

45080.name: Volcanic Eruption
45080.desc: Thrust your greatsword into the ground, inflicting <$MACRO magic @1:450800/> Damage. Hold for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>1.5s</FONT> to attack <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6</FONT> times to inflict <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 450801/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 450801/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 450801/>)/2)))*6/></FONT> Damage. Hit the Perfect Zone to deliver a finishing blow that inflicts <$MACRO magic @1:450802/> Damage and launches foes into the air.

45100.name: Cross Blade
45100.desc: Swing your greatsword in the shape of X, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:451001/> and <$MACRO physic @1:451001/> Damage for each swing.

45110.name: Flash Blade
45110.desc: Perform a diagonal slash to inflict <$MACRO physic @1:451100/> total Damage.

45190.name: Final Blow
45190.desc: Charge <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>4 meters</FONT> toward the target location and slash at foes, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:451900/> Damage and launching them into the air. Use as a combo to deliver a spinning attack, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:451901/> and <$MACRO physic @1:451901/> Damage before landing a downward blow, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:451902/> Damage.

45210.name: Flying Strike
45210.desc: Leap up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8 meters</FONT> to the target location and strike downward with your greatsword, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:452100/> Damage and knocking down foes.

45220.name: Wild Stomp
45220.desc: Stomp the ground with one foot to attack all foes within a <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>4-meter </FONT>radius inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:452200/> [Earth] Damage, inflicting Earthquake on them for <$MACRO bufftime_st @1:452203/>s.

45300.name: Fatal Sword
45300.desc: Thrust your greatsword down, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:453000/> Damage.

45600.name: Mountain Cleave
45600.desc: Jump while spinning counter-clockwise and smash the ground to create a storm of swords, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:456000/> Damage and knocking foes down.

45610.name: Spinning Sword
45610.desc: Swing your greatsword as you move, inflicting <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA ((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 456100/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 456100/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 456100/>)/2))*2/></FONT> Damage. Ignore collisions with Adventurers and Normal monsters while moving.

45620.name: Ground Smash
45620.desc: Thrust your greatsword into the ground, inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:456200/> Damage. Then pull it out and send forth a shockwave, pulling targets and inflicting <$MACRO physic @1:456210/> Damage.

45700.name: Punishing Draw
45700.desc: With your greatsword pinned to the ground, create a crack in the earth and raise it upwards. Deal <$MACRO physic @1:457000/> Damage and launch foes high into the air.

45710.name: Furious Claw
45710.desc: Menacingly slash your greatsword to the left and right and deal <$MACRO physic @1:457100/>, <$MACRO physic @1:457110/>, <$MACRO physic @1:457120/> Damage. Spin your body to attack and deal <$MACRO physic @1:457130/> Damage. Attack an airborne foe to launch them into the air again.

45720.name: Guillotine
45720.desc: Grab your greatsword in one hand and unleash all of your strength, dealing <$MACRO physic @1:457200/> Damage and launching foes into the air.

45730.name: Brutal Impact
45730.desc: Condense your rage's energy into your greatsword and put your weight into it as you strike the ground. Deal <$MACRO physic @1:457301/> Damage before Charging, and <$MACRO physic @1:457302/> Damage when Overcharged.

45740.name: Cruel Pierce
45740.desc: Hold your greatsword with one hand and stab with ferocious force to deal <$MACRO physic @1:457400/> Damage.

45800.name: Execute
45800.desc:
Concentrate your fury into your greatsword to produce a giant blade of rage. Perform an upward slash to deal <$MACRO physic @1:458000/> Damage, then jump up and slash <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>4</FONT> times to deal <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA ((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 458010/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 458010/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 458010/>)/2))*4/></FONT> total Damage before striking down. Each slash of the sword will leave a Sword Wound on the ground. All Sword Wounds explode with the last strike, dealing <$MACRO physic @1:458020/> Damage and launching foes into the air.
In Burst Mode, outgoing Damage +<FONT COLOR='#99ff99'>20%</FONT>.

45810.name: Ragna Break
45810.desc: Enter a state of extreme fury that manifests as a Flame Demon. Gather this furious energy into your greatsword and strike the earth, dealing <$MACRO physic @1:458100/> Damage and launching foes into the air.

32021.name: Float
32021.desc: Open your umbrella and fly forward <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>7 meters</FONT>. Press the key again to jump into the sky and land on the ground.

32030.name: Leap!
32030.desc: Instantly leap from downed position and land.

32110.name: Spread
32110.desc: Rapidly charge forward, piercing the target in front and inflicting <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321101/> Damage. On hit, open the umbrella, inflicting <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321102/> Damage.

32120.name: Rage
32120.desc: Perform a fierce swing and inflict <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321200/>Damage. Use the skill again to unsheathe a sword hidden in the umbrella and swing to inflict <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321201/> Damage.

32130.name: Downward Strike
32130.desc: Slam down the umbrella, inflicting <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321300/> Damage, then slam it down once more with greater force, inflicting <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321301/> Damage.

32140.name: Thick Fog
32140.desc: Unleash the umbrella's fog to unleash a shockwave, inflicting <$MACRO magic_ch @1:321403/> Damage, and move <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6 meters</FONT> backward. The fog lasts for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>5s</FONT>, attacking <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10</FONT> times, dealing up to <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 321401/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 321401/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 321401/>)/2))*10)*(<$TABLE_PC DamageCoefficient 603/>)/></FONT> damage, and for <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'><$CALC_COMMA %1 <$TABLE_SKILLBUFF Duration 321400/>/1000/>s</FONT>, Move Speed -<FONT COLOR='#99ff99'><$MACRO buffstat0_100 @1:321400/>%</FONT>, and inflicts Darkness.

32150.name: Rainstorm
32150.desc: Create a Rainstorm at the target location within <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>10 meters</FONT>. Inflicts a total of <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 321501/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 321501/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 321501/>)/2))*6)*(<$TABLE_PC DamageCoefficient 603/>)/></FONT> [Water] Damage to foes over <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>6</FONT> times for up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>3s</FONT>.

32160.name: Strong Wind
32160.desc: Swing the umbrella in the direction of the target location, summoning a penetrating wind that inflicts <$MACRO magic_ch @1:321603/> Damage to nearby foes. The wind strikes up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>5</FONT> times, inflicting a total of <FONT COLOR='#00ccff'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 321601/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 321601/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 321601/>)/2))*5)*(<$TABLE_PC DamageCoefficient 603/>)/></FONT> Damage and pushing them back.

32170.name: Tornado
32170.desc: Throw the umbrella in the direction of the target location, hitting the target up to <FONT COLOR='#ffff99'>8</FONT> times, inflicting a total of <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 321701/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 321701/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 321701/>)/2))*8)*(<$TABLE_PC DamageCoefficient 603/>)/></FONT> Damage. The spinning umbrella pushes the target away.

32180.name: Tornado Dance
32180.desc: Open up the umbrella and rapidly spin it while charging forward, inflicting a total of <FONT COLOR='#ffbb00'><$CALC_COMMA (((<$PLAYER_INFO STAT STAT_ATTACK_POWER/>)*(<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueF 321802/>/10000)+((<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueA 321802/> + <$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueB 321802/>)/2))*9)*(<$TABLE_PC DamageCoefficient 603/>)/></FONT> Damage. At the end, swing the umbrella with great force, inflicting <$MACRO physic_ch @1:321803/> Damage and pushing the foe away.

32190.name: Whirlpool
32190.desc: Create a Whirlpool in the direction of the target location.
